caption.p: Percentage repellency (PR) of the essential oil and its main constituents against L. serricorne after 2 h ( A) and 4 h ( B) treatment. Means in the same column followed by the same letters do not differ significantly ( p > 0.05) in ANOVA and Tukey’s tests. PR was subjected to an arcsine square-root transformation before ANOVA and Tukey’s tests.
